3. Classify Action Roll: If valid, assign the single most accurate skill check name (e.g., "Athletics", "Stealth", "Arcana", "Thieves' Tools") to 'roll_required'.
4. Establish DC: Set a balanced Difficulty Class (DC) matching standard 5e rules (5=Easy, 10=Medium, 15=Hard, 20=Very Hard) or use the room's explicit 'mechanics_override_json' value if provided.

